properties.Name: BeneficiaryStatusType
properties.Description:
The status of the Beneficiary., which is applied to a period of time.

Ex:
REMOVED
The Beneficiary was removed as beneficiary for the associated Policy and Policyholder.

MODIFIED
The Beneficiary was added or modified as beneficiary for the associated Policy and Policyholder.

ORIGINALLY-NAMED
The Beneficiary was originally named as beneficiary for the associated Policy and Policyholder.
